Text:
Looks like a great set, just in time for my birthday :) Thanks WMI!

I could completely understand too not wanting to pay for these anymore, it just seems sometimes that it's the same thing over and over. You have done a great thing for the time being though and I am sure you know a ton of us appreciate it more than words can describe.
good one wmi a bit of tit!what next?
I have another project I'm currently working on, so I'll let DigieraMandela do a resize version. Since he's so great at it :)
I hope you don't stop posting them anytime soon as nobody else seems to want to take your place. I also think your doing great work. Keep it up!
Is DigieraMandela downloading them as well or just downloading yours and re-sizing them?

It's $35 a month, which I don't make back. It's being promoted on the wmi site, but with no affiliate tied to it, it makes $0 in return. There is a donate button thrown up on the site, which uses paypal. I know some of you had offered to donate in the past, so if you're still up to it, go for it. Don't need to donate much. A few bucks from some of you would help, and it will continue to bring you sets.

I'm not saying you HAVE to donate or I'll stop uploading. I still haven't decided whether or not I'm going to stop, and more than likely I won't. Just saying it would be great if you guys wanna help out.

@ellafan

I think he downloads from me, then resizes and uploads them for all of you. Not sure if he has a membership or not. All I know is that he doesn't post his resizes until my torrents have 100's of seeds. Either way, he does a great service. I know a lot of people don't like the large file sizes.
Great job WMI, and about your comment wellcome to my world. +1
Looks like we got a donation. Will be renewing the membership, and 1 more month of FG sets.
Instead of resizing use VLC to batchconvert to Jpeg at 60% takes 2 minutes. The pictures stay the same size and quality, this 424mb becomes 99mb.
